1
00:01:03,920 --> 00:01:04,599
I'm so pissed off!

2
00:01:05,079 --> 00:01:05,480
Oh my.

3
00:01:05,959 --> 00:01:06,760
What's the matter?

4
00:01:06,760 --> 00:01:07,840
Young Prince.

5
00:01:08,719 --> 00:01:10,000
Things aren't going well, are they?

6
00:01:12,040 --> 00:01:13,000
Eunuch, don't worry.

7
00:01:13,519 --> 00:01:14,680
I just don't believe it.

8
00:01:14,879 --> 00:01:15,760
I refuse to believe

9
00:01:15,799 --> 00:01:17,560
they'd just watch the Prince of Chen die.

10
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:20,120
Young Prince...

11
00:01:21,239 --> 00:01:22,040
Although

12
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:23,079
the Crown Prince promised

13
00:01:23,079 --> 00:01:24,519
to hand the throne to you,

14
00:01:25,400 --> 00:01:26,159
but what if

15
00:01:26,159 --> 00:01:27,680
he changes his mind back at the palace

16
00:01:27,680 --> 00:01:29,040
and turns on you?

17
00:01:29,719 --> 00:01:31,319
What then?

18
00:01:32,400 --> 00:01:33,519
Eunuch, are you saying

19
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:34,760
my Royal Brother

20
00:01:34,920 --> 00:01:35,760
might go back on his word?

21
00:01:36,159 --> 00:01:36,319
Oh my.

22
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:36,840
Well...

23
00:01:37,159 --> 00:01:38,599
This Eunuch didn't say that.

24
00:01:39,719 --> 00:01:41,799
This old servant knows the Crown Prince,

25
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:43,640
and he probably wouldn't.

26
00:01:44,760 --> 00:01:45,560
But the world is unpredictable.

27
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:46,560
What if he does?

28
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,200
What?

29
00:01:51,359 --> 00:01:53,519
Still, I can't just watch my Royal Brother die!

30
00:01:54,159 --> 00:01:55,640
Heh heh heh.

31
00:01:55,959 --> 00:01:56,760
Young Prince,

32
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:58,000
calm yourself.

33
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:02,680
Since this old servant agreed to help the Twenty-Eighth Prince,

34
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:05,439
naturally I have a foolproof plan.

35
00:02:06,799 --> 00:02:07,599
Heh heh.

36
00:02:08,439 --> 00:02:09,240
Thank you for your kindness, Eunuch.

37
00:02:10,879 --> 00:02:11,680
But I wonder,

38
00:02:12,479 --> 00:02:14,560
what is this plan of yours?

39
00:02:14,599 --> 00:02:17,039
Of course, it's to ensure our Twenty-Eighth Prince

40
00:02:17,039 --> 00:02:21,319
takes the throne legitimately.

41
00:02:21,319 --> 00:02:22,039
Prince of Chen,

42
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,039
are you alright?

43
00:02:24,759 --> 00:02:25,680
It's just at my neck.

44
00:02:26,159 --> 00:02:27,639
I can hold on a while longer.

45
00:02:30,439 --> 00:02:31,599
Liu Heng is coming over.

46
00:02:31,719 --> 00:02:32,960
Maybe I should just agree for now.

47
00:02:32,960 --> 00:02:34,240
I don't want Royal Brother buried alive.

48
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:35,759
You can't.

49
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:37,039
You absolutely cannot.

50
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:39,759
Guards!

51
00:02:39,919 --> 00:02:40,479
Untie Qi Zhi.

52
00:02:41,639 --> 00:02:41,840
Huh?

53
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:48,919
Liu Heng,

54
00:02:49,080 --> 00:02:50,039
you captured us.

55
00:02:50,039 --> 00:02:51,120
What exactly are you trying to do?

56
00:02:51,719 --> 00:02:52,520
Oh.

57
00:02:53,639 --> 00:02:55,159
Because I suddenly felt

58
00:02:55,479 --> 00:02:57,000
making you watch Royal Brother die

59
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:57,639
would be a bit cruel.

60
00:02:58,280 --> 00:02:58,719
How about it?

61
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:00,400
I'm being good to you, right?

62
00:03:02,039 --> 00:03:02,520
Little Twenty-Eight,

63
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:04,159
I've made up my mind.

64
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:06,639
Since you want the throne so badly,

65
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:08,400
I'll hand it over to you.

66
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:09,319
Really?

67
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:11,560
Bring the brush and ink!

68
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,039
Oh my.

69
00:03:16,639 --> 00:03:18,000
If only you'd been this decisive earlier.

70
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:19,159
You wasted so much of everyone's time.

71
00:03:19,199 --> 00:03:19,599
Wait.

72
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:21,840
I'll write it for him.

73
00:03:25,599 --> 00:03:26,080
Hmm.

74
00:03:29,719 --> 00:03:31,000
Let's get one thing straight.

75
00:03:31,439 --> 00:03:32,439
The moment you get the decree,

76
00:03:32,639 --> 00:03:33,800
you must release Royal Brother.

77
00:03:34,400 --> 00:03:35,199
No problem.

78
00:03:35,199 --> 00:03:36,000
And Huahua.

79
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:38,039
And me.

80
00:03:38,159 --> 00:03:39,439
Oh, let me tell you,

81
00:03:39,879 --> 00:03:41,680
I never really wanted to kill any of you.

82
00:03:42,240 --> 00:03:42,960
So,

83
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:44,680
as long as you come quietly to the capital with me,

84
00:03:44,879 --> 00:03:45,800
I guarantee

85
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,439
you'll all be safe and sound.

86
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:54,759
By the Mandate of Heaven,

87
00:03:54,759 --> 00:03:56,080
a decree from the Crown Prince.

88
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,240
After this Crown Prince was forcibly named

89
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:59,039
heir to the throne by the late Emperor,

90
00:03:59,039 --> 00:03:59,240
the throne...

91
00:03:59,240 --> 00:04:02,159
Fearing my talents can't rule the realm,

92
00:04:02,159 --> 00:04:03,520
and the people would suffer,

93
00:04:03,719 --> 00:04:04,360
I cannot sleep at night,

94
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:05,759
nor rest by day.

95
00:04:06,319 --> 00:04:08,400
Fortunately, my Twenty-Eighth brother, Prince Kang Liu Heng,

96
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:11,560
excels in both letters and arms, a genius of governance.

97
00:04:11,879 --> 00:04:13,000
Are you satisfied now?

98
00:04:13,159 --> 00:04:14,159
Hurry up and release us.

99
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:15,919
No, no.

100
00:04:16,519 --> 00:04:18,399
Sign it, sign it!

101
00:04:28,879 --> 00:04:29,680
Heh heh.

102
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:31,680
Guards!

103
00:04:31,879 --> 00:04:33,959
Release them.

104
00:04:39,839 --> 00:04:41,959
Ah!

105
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:42,319
Don't move!

106
00:04:42,319 --> 00:04:43,199
Oh no!

107
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:44,759
Ah!

108
00:04:45,199 --> 00:04:46,079
Stop yelling!

109
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:48,959
P-p-put the swords down!

110
00:04:49,639 --> 00:04:50,680
All of you, put them down!

111
00:04:51,079 --> 00:04:51,680
Drop them!

112
00:04:54,839 --> 00:04:57,360
A-and release the Prince of Chen too!

113
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,600
Let him go!

114
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:01,800
Hurry!

115
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:05,040
Faster!

116
00:05:05,199 --> 00:05:06,040
Let's talk this out calmly.

117
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:09,839
Go, quickly!

118
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:10,720
Hurry up!

119
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:11,519
Don't move!

120
00:05:11,720 --> 00:05:11,879
Stay back!

121
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:12,560
Don't come any closer!

122
00:05:13,199 --> 00:05:13,639
One more move...

123
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:15,040
Move again and...

124
00:05:15,839 --> 00:05:16,639
Don't move!

125
00:05:16,639 --> 00:05:17,439
Stay back!

126
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,040
Don't come over!

127
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:20,720
Come closer and I'll...

128
00:05:31,959 --> 00:05:33,600
Put that thing down before you talk.

129
00:05:33,600 --> 00:05:33,839
Put that thing down before you talk!

130
00:05:33,959 --> 00:05:34,199
Ah!

131
00:05:37,519 --> 00:05:38,519
That Ouyang Yan...

132
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:39,759
She's gone way too far!

133
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:42,040
One day I'll settle the score with her.

134
00:05:44,000 --> 00:05:45,759
Young Prince, nice acting.

135
00:05:45,759 --> 00:05:46,439
Ah!

136
00:05:47,399 --> 00:05:48,680
Those guys...

137
00:05:48,839 --> 00:05:51,639
They actually think they escaped on their own.

138
00:05:51,639 --> 00:05:52,120
Hmph.

139
00:05:53,279 --> 00:05:55,199
They still think they rescued the older brother.

140
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:56,680
Eunuch Gao,

141
00:05:57,480 --> 00:05:59,319
your Deceitful Switch trick

142
00:05:59,319 --> 00:06:01,079
was absolutely brilliant!

143
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:02,360
Ah,

144
00:06:02,519 --> 00:06:03,319
from now on,

145
00:06:03,319 --> 00:06:04,759
I'll be relying on you, Eunuch.

146
00:06:04,800 --> 00:06:05,360
Mm.

147
00:06:05,839 --> 00:06:06,720
Of course.

148
00:06:07,959 --> 00:06:08,759
Alright then,

149
00:06:10,079 --> 00:06:11,639
since things have come to this,

150
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:12,439
I'll just

151
00:06:12,439 --> 00:06:13,759
take the real Prince of Chen

152
00:06:13,759 --> 00:06:14,480
back to the palace.

153
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:14,759
Ah?

154
00:06:14,759 --> 00:06:15,399
Hey, hey, hey!

155
00:06:15,399 --> 00:06:15,879
No, no, no.

156
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:16,920
Eunuch Gao.

157
00:06:17,079 --> 00:06:17,879
Hmm?

158
00:06:18,240 --> 00:06:20,360
The journey back to the capital is long.

159
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:21,879
It'd be inconvenient for you to bring him along.

160
00:06:21,920 --> 00:06:22,759
It's fine.

161
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:25,040
Nothing inconvenient about it.

162
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:27,600
Besides,

163
00:06:27,639 --> 00:06:28,439
how could I

164
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:31,199
trouble you, Young Prince, over him?

165
00:06:31,199 --> 00:06:31,879
Hmm.

166
00:06:31,879 --> 00:06:32,639
Ha ha ha!

167
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:33,879
No trouble at all!

168
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:34,560
Eunuch Gao,

169
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:35,839
just consider it

170
00:06:35,839 --> 00:06:37,240
me easing your burden.

171
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:40,800
What's this?

172
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,600
By the look on your face,

173
00:06:42,800 --> 00:06:43,720
are you displeased?

174
00:06:46,079 --> 00:06:46,839
Or perhaps

175
00:06:47,079 --> 00:06:48,480
you don't trust This Prince?

176
00:06:48,639 --> 00:06:49,439
Of course not!

177
00:06:50,399 --> 00:06:51,360
Am I displeased?

178
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:52,079
Hey, hey, hey.

179
00:06:52,079 --> 00:06:53,160
Am I displeased?

180
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:56,680
Not at all.

181
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:58,399
I'm not displeased.

182
00:06:58,639 --> 00:06:59,680
How could I be displeased?

183
00:07:00,279 --> 00:07:01,639
Young Prince, you misunderstand.

184
00:07:02,720 --> 00:07:03,519
Alright.

185
00:07:04,319 --> 00:07:06,160
Then I'll trouble you, Young Prince.

186
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:06,600
Ah.

187
00:07:07,319 --> 00:07:08,399
I take my leave.

188
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:12,839
Take care, Eunuch.

189
00:07:25,439 --> 00:07:26,920
Oh my!

190
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:27,839
Hmph!

191
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:33,680
Phew.

192
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:35,279
We finally got away.

193
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:37,079
That really scared me back there.

194
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:38,560
That Liu Heng.

195
00:07:39,120 --> 00:07:41,160
I'll beat him up every time I see him.

196
00:07:41,560 --> 00:07:43,519
Enough, you've tormented him plenty.

197
00:07:46,759 --> 00:07:47,480
Everyone,

198
00:07:47,839 --> 00:07:48,720
are you all okay?

199
00:07:50,160 --> 00:07:51,199
Royal Brother, are you alright?

200
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:53,920
Ah...

201
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:56,079
I'm so hungry.

202
00:07:57,160 --> 00:07:57,920
Oh right.

203
00:07:58,079 --> 00:07:59,560
Huahua hasn't eaten yet.

204
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:02,160
Tch.

205
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:03,759
The rest of us are starving,

206
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,240
but Huahua never misses a meal.

207
00:08:05,240 --> 00:08:05,920
Hehe.

208
00:08:07,759 --> 00:08:08,560
Huahua.

209
00:08:09,199 --> 00:08:10,959
Ah.

210
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:15,120
Don't be like that.

211
00:08:15,439 --> 00:08:16,839
The Prince of Chen isn't that kind of person.

212
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,879
I don't care what kind of person he is.

213
00:08:18,879 --> 00:08:20,079
But since he won't save Huahua,

214
00:08:20,079 --> 00:08:21,160
then I'll go myself.

215
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:21,920
Hey!

216
00:08:22,040 --> 00:08:23,279
You don't know any martial arts.

217
00:08:23,319 --> 00:08:24,920
Going there is basically suicide.

218
00:08:26,279 --> 00:08:27,639
Then I'll die together with Huahua.

219
00:08:27,639 --> 00:08:28,519
Then I'll go with you.

220
00:08:28,519 --> 00:08:29,199
No.

221
00:08:29,879 --> 00:08:30,720
Why not?

222
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:32,919
Don't we always take things on together?

223
00:08:33,879 --> 00:08:35,360
You're about to become the Empress.

224
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:36,879
I shouldn't drag you into fights.

225
00:08:37,320 --> 00:08:38,120
I...

226
00:08:42,519 --> 00:08:43,320
Hmm?

227
00:08:43,759 --> 00:08:44,639
Liu Heng?

228
00:08:44,960 --> 00:08:45,759
Where?

229
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:47,919
Huh?

230
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:50,639
Hey.

231
00:08:50,799 --> 00:08:52,240
It really does look like him.

232
00:08:52,279 --> 00:08:53,120
Let's go check.

233
00:08:58,120 --> 00:08:59,000
Who's there?

234
00:08:59,080 --> 00:09:00,039
Eunuch Gao.

235
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:03,159
Young Prince.

236
00:09:03,399 --> 00:09:05,799
What brings the Young Prince here?

237
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:07,639
Didn't this old servant tell Young Prince

238
00:09:07,639 --> 00:09:09,720
to wait for news in Kangcheng?

239
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:12,799
The Coronation Ceremony is just days away.

240
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:15,320
This Prince simply couldn't rest easy.

241
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:17,600
What's there to worry about?

242
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:19,960
Could it be

243
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:22,639
the Young Prince still doesn't trust this old servant?

244
00:09:23,120 --> 00:09:23,720
Come on.

245
00:09:23,879 --> 00:09:26,159
When have I ever doubted you, Eunuch Gao?

246
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,080
Hmm.

247
00:09:27,799 --> 00:09:30,080
I just can't help worrying the Prince of Chen

248
00:09:31,159 --> 00:09:32,440
might go back on his word.

249
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:33,159
Oh my.

250
00:09:33,159 --> 00:09:35,080
There's nothing to worry about.

251
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:36,399
Young Prince,

252
00:09:37,159 --> 00:09:38,639
you just put your mind

253
00:09:38,639 --> 00:09:40,759
completely at ease.

254
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:43,120
He's just a transitional figure.

255
00:09:43,519 --> 00:09:44,840
A few days after he takes the throne,

256
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:47,320
I'll find some excuse

257
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:50,639
to have him pass the throne to you legitimately.

258
00:09:50,759 --> 00:09:51,559
Really?

259
00:09:51,559 --> 00:09:52,159
Mm-hmm.

260
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:53,039
Thank you, Eunuch.

261
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:57,000
But will the Prince of Chen

262
00:09:58,159 --> 00:09:59,720
really step down obediently?

263
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:03,360
The Young Prince needn't trouble himself with that.

264
00:10:03,679 --> 00:10:05,360
Just leave it to this old servant.

265
00:10:05,440 --> 00:10:06,039
Hahaha.

266
00:10:06,279 --> 00:10:07,399
Young Prince,

267
00:10:07,679 --> 00:10:09,120
in this old servant's heart,

268
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:10,519
only you

269
00:10:10,759 --> 00:10:13,279
are the one true choice for the throne.

270
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:16,080
Eunuch.

271
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:17,879
Well, since that's the case,

272
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,080
for the next few days,

273
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:21,080
this Prince will stay at the palace.

274
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,840
It'll be easier to keep in touch with you.

275
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:24,360
That's not quite convenient,

276
00:10:24,759 --> 00:10:25,360
Your Highness.

277
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:28,240
There are many Imperial concubines here.

278
00:10:28,559 --> 00:10:30,000
If you move in just like that,

279
00:10:30,039 --> 00:10:32,200
others will start suspecting you, Your Highness.

280
00:10:32,320 --> 00:10:33,120
Never mind.

281
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:34,360
Let them suspect.

282
00:10:35,159 --> 00:10:35,960
Then this Prince

283
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:37,120
will take his leave first.

284
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,600
Safe travels, Your Highness.

285
00:10:42,320 --> 00:10:44,679
What on earth goes on in that head of his?

286
00:10:45,039 --> 00:10:45,639
Ugh.

287
00:10:51,879 --> 00:10:53,000
Who are you people?

288
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:55,559
What are you doing with that blade?

289
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:58,279
Ask the King of Hell after you're dead.

290
00:11:19,919 --> 00:11:20,720
Where's Huahua?

291
00:11:21,080 --> 00:11:22,120
What Huahua?

292
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:23,879
I'm not telling you.

293
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:37,000
Wait, isn't this...

294
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:41,840
He's trying to kill me!

295
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:43,279
You know him?

296
00:11:46,240 --> 00:11:47,360
I saw him before at Eunuch Gao's place.

297
00:11:50,279 --> 00:11:51,360
Why is he trying to kill you?

298
00:11:54,559 --> 00:11:55,879
He's literally trying to kill you,

299
00:11:55,879 --> 00:11:57,519
and you're still keeping his secret?

300
00:11:58,799 --> 00:12:00,360
Have you ever heard the saying?

301
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:05,080
Enemies and friends are only a step apart.

302
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:06,679
Just like love and hate,

303
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:09,080
separated by the thinnest line.

304
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,039
Nope.

305
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:14,159
Have you ever heard this saying?

306
00:12:14,159 --> 00:12:15,200
The enemy of my enemy

307
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:16,240
is my friend.

308
00:12:16,240 --> 00:12:16,480
Enough.

309
00:12:16,480 --> 00:12:16,919
Stop preaching.

310
00:12:21,120 --> 00:12:21,600
Eunuch.

311
00:12:22,519 --> 00:12:22,919
Go.

312
00:12:23,919 --> 00:12:25,480
We've crossed the river,

313
00:12:25,639 --> 00:12:27,440
so it's time to burn the bridge.

314
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:28,159
Yes.

315
00:12:29,240 --> 00:12:29,840
Guards!

316
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:31,399
Go tear down the bridge south of the city.

317
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:39,559
The Prince of Chen is with me.

318
00:12:39,679 --> 00:12:41,639
And that chicken is with Eunuch Gao.

319
00:12:47,559 --> 00:12:48,360
Royal Brother!

320
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:49,879
Liu Heng!

321
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:51,440
Royal Brother!

322
00:12:51,440 --> 00:12:52,399
Let go, let go, let go!

323
00:12:52,399 --> 00:12:53,559
We're on the same side now.

324
00:12:53,919 --> 00:12:54,600
What do you mean?

325
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:55,879
Come on, let go!

326
00:12:55,919 --> 00:12:56,720
Here's the plan.

327
00:12:56,759 --> 00:12:57,759
We'll stay here to figure out a strategy.

328
00:12:57,759 --> 00:12:58,799
You go and inform the Crown Prince.

329
00:12:58,799 --> 00:13:00,200
You wouldn't be much help here anyway.

330
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:02,440
Oh.

331
00:13:06,039 --> 00:13:06,639
Hey.

332
00:13:07,679 --> 00:13:10,080
Why don't you keep Huahua by your side too?

333
00:13:10,159 --> 00:13:11,159
I'm scared!

334
00:13:11,279 --> 00:13:12,879
Fine, hit me, hit me, hit me.

335
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:13,919
Just don't kill me.

336
00:13:13,919 --> 00:13:14,639
Go on, hit me.

337
00:13:17,279 --> 00:13:18,200
Your Highness, Crown Prince.

338
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:20,159
Princess Ouyang Yan of Yan Kingdom is here.

339
00:13:20,960 --> 00:13:21,759
Ouyang Yan?

340
00:13:21,879 --> 00:13:22,720
Show her in at once.

341
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:24,720
Crown Prince!

342
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:25,360
This is bad!

343
00:13:25,360 --> 00:13:25,960
Eunuch Gao,

344
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:26,559
Eunuch Gao, he...

345
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:28,159
Greetings, Princess.

346
00:13:30,679 --> 00:13:31,559
Teacher is one of us.

347
00:13:31,759 --> 00:13:32,600
Speak freely.

348
00:13:33,960 --> 00:13:34,799
I'm back!

349
00:13:35,039 --> 00:13:35,559
You're back.

350
00:13:35,559 --> 00:13:35,919
Mm.

351
00:13:37,120 --> 00:13:38,840
Have you come up with a plan?

352
00:13:40,039 --> 00:13:41,039
Nothing yet.

353
00:13:42,759 --> 00:13:44,480
Eunuch Gao is a veteran of the previous court.

354
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:45,879
He's high in rank and powerful.

355
00:13:46,519 --> 00:13:48,360
And we don't have any solid evidence.

356
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:50,000
Just our word against his,

357
00:13:50,120 --> 00:13:51,639
it'll be hard to bring him down.

358
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:52,639
That's right.

359
00:13:53,879 --> 00:13:55,519
Plus, Eunuch Gao is plotting rebellion,

360
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:57,600
and he's built quite a network at court.

361
00:13:58,600 --> 00:14:00,279
If we confront him head-on,

362
00:14:01,519 --> 00:14:02,759
we'll definitely lose badly.

363
00:14:04,360 --> 00:14:05,960
So what do we do now?

364
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:08,039
The Grand Secretary told us to relay a message.

365
00:14:08,039 --> 00:14:08,840
Mm?

366
00:14:09,200 --> 00:14:10,000
Teacher.

367
00:14:10,080 --> 00:14:10,600
Mm.

368
00:14:10,799 --> 00:14:11,600
He said...

369
00:14:11,639 --> 00:14:12,879
Uh...

370
00:14:13,600 --> 00:14:15,440
Something about giving people their, uh, own way back.

371
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:19,159
Teacher truly lives up to his name.

372
00:14:19,519 --> 00:14:22,679
A brilliant taste of their own medicine!

373
00:14:23,360 --> 00:14:24,080
Yes, yes, yes.

374
00:14:24,080 --> 00:14:24,879
That's the one.

375
00:14:25,759 --> 00:14:27,840
What are you all talking about?

376
00:14:27,840 --> 00:14:28,960
It's simple.

377
00:14:29,399 --> 00:14:31,120
Since he swapped the older brother for the younger,

378
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:32,480
we'll do the same thing right back.

379
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:34,440
Swap the older brother back for the younger.

380
00:14:34,519 --> 00:14:35,840
Once he takes the throne,

381
00:14:35,840 --> 00:14:37,600
bringing down Eunuch Gao

382
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:40,480
will be as easy as flipping a hand.

383
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:42,240
Exactly.

384
00:14:44,080 --> 00:14:45,480
Once you've brought down Eunuch Gao,

385
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:46,919
you can make me Emperor.

386
00:14:47,039 --> 00:14:48,120
Perfect!

387
00:14:48,159 --> 00:14:49,360
That's not part of our plan.

388
00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:50,120
Thank you.

389
00:14:50,440 --> 00:14:51,240
Eunuch.

390
00:14:51,519 --> 00:14:54,519
The men sent to kill Liu Heng haven't returned.

391
00:14:54,559 --> 00:14:57,200
Could I have underestimated him?

392
00:14:57,200 --> 00:14:57,879
Eunuch.

393
00:14:58,159 --> 00:14:58,840
The Crown Prince

394
00:14:58,840 --> 00:15:00,320
is waiting for you to taste his food.

395
00:15:00,679 --> 00:15:01,799
I know, I know.

396
00:15:26,600 --> 00:15:27,399
Your Highness.

397
00:15:27,679 --> 00:15:29,120
Princess Ouyang Yan of Yan Kingdom

398
00:15:29,120 --> 00:15:30,720
invites you over for a game of Go.

399
00:15:32,799 --> 00:15:33,960
She knows how to play?

400
00:15:34,720 --> 00:15:35,519
Hmph.

401
00:15:36,039 --> 00:15:36,759
The Princess also said

402
00:15:36,759 --> 00:15:37,279
that her brother

403
00:15:37,279 --> 00:15:39,399
brought you a Go manual from Yan Kingdom.

404
00:15:39,919 --> 00:15:41,879
She's sure Your Highness will like it.

405
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:47,440
Your Highness.

406
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:49,159
This old servant has arrived.

407
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:52,200
You may withdraw for now.

408
00:15:53,600 --> 00:15:54,200
Yes.

409
00:16:08,919 --> 00:16:09,360
Oh.

410
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:11,000
The Book of Songs?

411
00:16:11,360 --> 00:16:12,480
Since when, Your Highness,

412
00:16:12,679 --> 00:16:14,320
have you taken such interest in copying it?

413
00:16:16,679 --> 00:16:18,279
I've been restless and irritable lately.

414
00:16:18,519 --> 00:16:19,320
Copying the Book of Songs

415
00:16:19,919 --> 00:16:21,120
helps with self-cultivation.

416
00:16:21,960 --> 00:16:22,440
Ah.

417
00:16:22,639 --> 00:16:24,080
The Book of Songs is fine, of course,

418
00:16:24,679 --> 00:16:27,279
but Your Highness has Your precious body.

419
00:16:27,559 --> 00:16:28,960
Staying up so late

420
00:16:29,039 --> 00:16:30,440
could ruin your health. What then?

421
00:16:32,720 --> 00:16:33,759
In just a few more days,

422
00:16:34,120 --> 00:16:35,840
I won't have Your precious body anymore.

423
00:16:36,759 --> 00:16:37,919
Even you, Eunuch Gao,

424
00:16:38,440 --> 00:16:39,840
will be serving someone else.

425
00:16:40,200 --> 00:16:41,000
Isn't that right?

426
00:16:43,480 --> 00:16:44,600
Your Highness,

427
00:16:45,720 --> 00:16:49,799
this old servant watched you grow up.

428
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:51,519
In this old servant's heart,

429
00:16:51,600 --> 00:16:54,360
you will always be the Crown Prince.

430
00:16:56,240 --> 00:16:57,039
Well, in that case,

431
00:16:57,720 --> 00:17:00,200
keep me company and copy more sutras.

432
00:17:17,400 --> 00:17:18,480
Done.

433
00:17:28,039 --> 00:17:28,799
Ugh.

434
00:17:29,039 --> 00:17:30,640
One just left and another shows up.

435
00:17:31,759 --> 00:17:32,519
I have to say,

436
00:17:32,799 --> 00:17:34,960
why do you have to hide him with me?

437
00:17:35,680 --> 00:17:36,559
The most dangerous place

438
00:17:36,559 --> 00:17:37,799
is the safest place.

439
00:17:38,319 --> 00:17:39,960
Have you forgotten

440
00:17:39,960 --> 00:17:40,799
how they treated you?

441
00:17:41,319 --> 00:17:42,400
We hand him over to you

442
00:17:42,680 --> 00:17:43,119
and you're still not happy?

443
00:17:44,119 --> 00:17:45,240
I'm not happy.

444
00:17:45,240 --> 00:17:46,440
Not happy, not happy, not happy!

445
00:17:46,720 --> 00:17:47,880
I'm extremely unhappy.

446
00:17:48,759 --> 00:17:49,480
You two, listen,

447
00:17:49,759 --> 00:17:50,799
you won't let me be emperor,

448
00:17:51,160 --> 00:17:52,559
yet keep asking me to help you.

449
00:17:52,880 --> 00:17:54,000
You've got some nerve!

450
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:55,640
You'll help whether you want to or not.

451
00:17:56,680 --> 00:17:58,720
You'll help whether you want to or not.

452
00:17:59,519 --> 00:18:00,000
Hmph.

453
00:18:00,559 --> 00:18:01,440
In the morning,

454
00:18:01,519 --> 00:18:02,680
you had bird's nest porridge.

455
00:18:02,680 --> 00:18:03,279
At noon,

456
00:18:03,279 --> 00:18:04,279
you had a whole-fish banquet.

457
00:18:04,279 --> 00:18:05,799
At night, you said you'd study the Go manual,

458
00:18:05,799 --> 00:18:06,880
so you had no appetite for dinner.

459
00:18:06,880 --> 00:18:09,920
You only ate a little bit of pastry.

460
00:18:09,960 --> 00:18:11,880
Lord Liu sent you a Jade ruyi.

461
00:18:11,880 --> 00:18:13,400
You absolutely loved it at the time

462
00:18:13,400 --> 00:18:14,440
and said one line:

463
00:18:14,720 --> 00:18:16,319
"I hope this Jade ruyi

464
00:18:16,400 --> 00:18:18,920
truly brings me what I wish."

465
00:18:18,920 --> 00:18:19,680
When you said that,

466
00:18:19,680 --> 00:18:20,440
Eunuch Gao was present.

467
00:18:20,440 --> 00:18:21,319
Memorize it cold!

468
00:18:21,440 --> 00:18:22,200
After that,

469
00:18:22,200 --> 00:18:23,440
you went to the Imperial Garden

470
00:18:23,440 --> 00:18:25,079
and praised a palace lantern

471
00:18:25,079 --> 00:18:26,400
to no end.

472
00:18:26,400 --> 00:18:27,359
Eunuch Gao was present.

473
00:18:27,359 --> 00:18:29,200
Remember, it's a palace lantern.

474
00:18:29,640 --> 00:18:30,079
Hey,

475
00:18:30,079 --> 00:18:31,599
you're throwing so much at me at once,

476
00:18:31,640 --> 00:18:32,880
how can I possibly remember?

477
00:18:33,279 --> 00:18:35,000
You have to, even if you can't.

478
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:35,720
I went through a lot

479
00:18:35,720 --> 00:18:37,240
to drag this out of your brother.

480
00:18:37,240 --> 00:18:38,000
One wrong word

481
00:18:38,000 --> 00:18:39,640
and the whole thing falls apart.

482
00:18:39,640 --> 00:18:40,400
You memorize Go manuals so well,

483
00:18:40,400 --> 00:18:41,200
but can't remember this?

484
00:18:41,200 --> 00:18:41,480
Keep going.

485
00:18:41,640 --> 00:18:42,839
On the way, a little eunuch

486
00:18:42,839 --> 00:18:44,240
bumped into you while walking.

487
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:46,119
Eunuch Gao gave him thirty lashes.

488
00:18:46,119 --> 00:18:47,079
Note, it's thirty,

489
00:18:47,079 --> 00:18:47,960
not 28, not 29,

490
00:18:47,960 --> 00:18:48,920
it's 30!

491
00:18:49,000 --> 00:18:49,759
Eunuch Gao has arrived!

492
00:18:49,839 --> 00:18:50,720
Eunuch Gao is here.

493
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:51,920
Why is Eunuch Gao here?

494
00:18:52,319 --> 00:18:52,720
I need to hide.

495
00:18:52,720 --> 00:18:53,119
Hide!

496
00:18:53,480 --> 00:18:54,279
No good, can't hide here.

497
00:18:54,279 --> 00:18:55,039
Oh, behind there!

498
00:18:55,160 --> 00:18:55,960
Too small!

499
00:18:56,240 --> 00:18:58,519
I'm done for, done for!

500
00:18:58,599 --> 00:18:59,599
Hey, wait a minute.

501
00:19:00,279 --> 00:19:01,319
I don't need to hide.

502
00:19:01,680 --> 00:19:02,640
I don't know anything.

503
00:19:02,680 --> 00:19:03,519
I thought you were...

504
00:19:03,880 --> 00:19:04,720
Where's Liu Xiaoyao?

505
00:19:05,920 --> 00:19:06,920
I'm here to see Liu Xiaoyao.

506
00:19:06,920 --> 00:19:07,759
To see Liu Xiaoyao

507
00:19:08,799 --> 00:19:10,759
about the pre-coronation details.

508
00:19:11,039 --> 00:19:12,079
Mm, come, come, come.

509
00:19:13,519 --> 00:19:14,519
Prince of Chen,

510
00:19:14,680 --> 00:19:17,039
Shall we serve Daughter's Red at the pre-coronation banquet?

511
00:19:17,039 --> 00:19:17,680
Your Highness.

512
00:19:19,960 --> 00:19:20,119
Qi...

513
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:22,759
Special Envoy Qi, you're here too.

514
00:19:24,039 --> 00:19:24,839
Eunuch Gao.

515
00:19:26,319 --> 00:19:27,119
Your Highness.

516
00:19:27,680 --> 00:19:29,640
Yesterday, this old servant saw Your Highness

517
00:19:29,680 --> 00:19:32,359
took a particular interest in an incense burner.

518
00:19:32,440 --> 00:19:35,000
So I had someone steal it for you.

519
00:19:35,119 --> 00:19:37,240
Bring it in for His Highness.

520
00:19:38,079 --> 00:19:39,039
An incense burner?

521
00:19:39,880 --> 00:19:40,599
Oh my.

522
00:19:40,599 --> 00:19:42,000
Some people really

523
00:19:42,319 --> 00:19:44,039
know how to read the situation.

524
00:19:44,039 --> 00:19:44,799
Right, Xiang...

525
00:19:45,039 --> 00:19:45,920
Right, Prince of Chen?

526
00:19:46,039 --> 00:19:49,039
It's a token of this old servant's regard for Your Highness.

527
00:19:49,559 --> 00:19:52,160
Hahaha.

528
00:19:52,160 --> 00:19:53,039
Oh dear.

529
00:19:53,839 --> 00:19:55,119
It seems Eunuch Gao

530
00:19:55,400 --> 00:19:57,039
is getting on in years.

531
00:19:57,240 --> 00:19:58,200
That mind of yours,

532
00:19:58,200 --> 00:19:59,559
your memory isn't what it used to be.

533
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:01,160
As I recall,

534
00:20:01,759 --> 00:20:03,519
what I clearly said yesterday was

535
00:20:03,519 --> 00:20:05,440
I had my eye on a palace lantern.

536
00:20:06,759 --> 00:20:09,160
So why did you bring me an incense burner?

537
00:20:09,599 --> 00:20:10,319
Huh?

538
00:20:15,119 --> 00:20:16,400
Ah!

539
00:20:18,200 --> 00:20:19,720
Oh no.

540
00:20:20,079 --> 00:20:20,920
Your Highness.

541
00:20:21,440 --> 00:20:23,440
This old servant is getting old.

542
00:20:23,599 --> 00:20:24,960
When you get on in years,

543
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:26,440
it's easy to slip.

544
00:20:26,599 --> 00:20:27,359
So,

545
00:20:27,359 --> 00:20:29,960
the elderly must wear proper shoes.

546
00:20:30,039 --> 00:20:31,440
They must be breathable,

547
00:20:31,599 --> 00:20:32,920
to prevent falls.

548
00:20:32,920 --> 00:20:33,640
What are you doing?

549
00:20:36,119 --> 00:20:37,559
And memory tends to fail.

550
00:20:37,559 --> 00:20:38,279
Heh heh heh.

551
00:20:38,279 --> 00:20:39,000
Your Highness.

552
00:20:39,000 --> 00:20:40,880
This old servant remembered wrong.

553
00:20:41,160 --> 00:20:42,559
A palace lantern.

554
00:20:43,039 --> 00:20:44,400
This old servant will go

555
00:20:44,480 --> 00:20:45,640
fetch a palace lantern for you right away.

556
00:20:45,720 --> 00:20:47,000
This old servant takes his leave.

557
00:20:47,599 --> 00:20:48,720
Mm.

558
00:20:54,519 --> 00:20:56,400
An incense burner.

559
00:20:58,079 --> 00:21:00,680
Good thing I came prepared, right?

560
00:21:00,680 --> 00:21:01,440
Hey,

561
00:21:01,559 --> 00:21:02,680
He didn't catch on, did he?

562
00:21:02,880 --> 00:21:04,000
How could he possibly catch on?

563
00:21:04,000 --> 00:21:04,440
Hey,

564
00:21:04,440 --> 00:21:04,640
Carry on.

565
00:21:05,880 --> 00:21:09,240
Last night, you went to the brothel.

566
00:21:10,359 --> 00:21:11,079
This is bizarre.

567
00:21:12,079 --> 00:21:13,240
This guy here is the older brother.

568
00:21:13,319 --> 00:21:15,200
Just watch me drag his little brother out.

569
00:21:15,200 --> 00:21:15,880
Eunuch,

570
00:21:16,119 --> 00:21:16,960
going that far.

571
00:21:23,160 --> 00:21:24,559
That damn bookworm.

572
00:21:24,960 --> 00:21:27,200
Didn't we agree on A taste of their own medicine?

573
00:21:27,839 --> 00:21:28,319
Fine then.

574
00:21:29,000 --> 00:21:30,640
I'll use your own tactics, Qi Zhi,

575
00:21:30,680 --> 00:21:32,079
and turn them right back on you.

576
00:21:32,559 --> 00:21:34,000
When you come back and see him here,

577
00:21:34,480 --> 00:21:35,640
let's see if you're surprised,

578
00:21:35,640 --> 00:21:36,519
or shocked.

579
00:21:49,799 --> 00:21:50,960
Ugh.

580
00:21:51,559 --> 00:21:55,319
These eyebrows are so hard to draw.

581
00:22:02,960 --> 00:22:03,400
Brother.

582
00:22:04,279 --> 00:22:05,079
Yan'er.

583
00:22:05,400 --> 00:22:06,640
I have to return to the Yan Kingdom.

584
00:22:06,839 --> 00:22:07,640
Right now?

585
00:22:10,039 --> 00:22:11,880
You're not staying for my wedding?

586
00:22:19,920 --> 00:22:21,759
Father just received an urgent letter from Daliang.

587
00:22:21,960 --> 00:22:23,839
Dubian Kingdom fully invaded Yan Kingdom.

588
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:26,440
Generals Zhang and Shangguan have both fallen.

589
00:22:27,799 --> 00:22:29,880
Father's illness has grown much worse.

590
00:22:30,119 --> 00:22:31,519
I must head back at once.

591
00:22:32,720 --> 00:22:33,799
I'll go back with you.

592
00:22:34,960 --> 00:22:35,680
No.

593
00:22:36,599 --> 00:22:37,440
You must stay.

594
00:22:39,200 --> 00:22:40,799
You must become Empress of Daliang.

595
00:22:41,559 --> 00:22:42,880
Only then can you bring Daliang's troops

596
00:22:42,880 --> 00:22:44,759
to save our people of Yan Kingdom from this misery.

597
00:22:46,000 --> 00:22:47,559
But I don't want to be Empress.

598
00:22:47,799 --> 00:22:48,519
Brother.

599
00:22:49,119 --> 00:22:49,920
Just let me go back with you.

600
00:22:50,279 --> 00:22:50,720
Ouyang Yan,

601
00:22:53,359 --> 00:22:54,279
Do you realize

602
00:22:55,720 --> 00:22:57,759
that every citizen of Yan Kingdom right now,

603
00:22:58,079 --> 00:22:58,880
their hope

604
00:23:00,000 --> 00:23:00,759
rests entirely on you?

605
00:23:05,039 --> 00:23:05,839
Remember,

606
00:23:06,680 --> 00:23:08,279
Until you become Empress,

607
00:23:09,119 --> 00:23:11,599
don't breathe a word of this to anyone.

608
00:23:13,559 --> 00:23:14,359
I understand.

609
00:23:16,880 --> 00:23:17,759
Don't worry.

610
00:23:31,440 --> 00:23:31,799
Goodness.

611
00:23:31,799 --> 00:23:34,200
I've been busy with Prince of Chen all day.

612
00:23:34,200 --> 00:23:35,720
Why summon me this late?

613
00:23:36,759 --> 00:23:37,559
No reason.

614
00:23:38,200 --> 00:23:39,200
Just want to chat with you.

615
00:23:39,200 --> 00:23:39,960
Is that not allowed?

616
00:23:40,920 --> 00:23:42,720
Didn't you say it was important?

617
00:23:43,839 --> 00:23:46,000
This Princess wishing to chat with you,

618
00:23:46,000 --> 00:23:46,839
Isn't that important enough?

619
00:23:49,359 --> 00:23:50,240
Fine, fine, fine.

620
00:23:51,039 --> 00:23:51,839
Oh my.

621
00:23:52,079 --> 00:23:53,519
The noble Princess of Yan Kingdom

622
00:23:53,519 --> 00:23:55,640
willing to chat with a chicken farmer.

623
00:23:55,680 --> 00:23:56,839
What an honor of three lifetimes.

624
00:23:57,240 --> 00:23:57,960
Let's chat.

625
00:24:00,200 --> 00:24:00,920
Hey.

626
00:24:07,319 --> 00:24:08,880
Didn't you say we'd chat?

627
00:24:08,880 --> 00:24:09,880
Why aren't you saying anything?

628
00:24:10,759 --> 00:24:11,559
Oh.

629
00:24:12,279 --> 00:24:14,200
This humble commoner isn't worthy to chat.

630
00:24:17,680 --> 00:24:19,559
Honestly, I rather envy this humble commoner.

631
00:24:21,440 --> 00:24:23,519
At least you can do whatever

632
00:24:23,559 --> 00:24:24,599
you want to do.

633
00:24:27,599 --> 00:24:28,359
Oh please.

634
00:24:28,359 --> 00:24:29,960
Back when I was studying as a kid,

635
00:24:30,319 --> 00:24:31,880
I was too poor to even afford paper.

636
00:24:32,599 --> 00:24:34,720
Then I finally passed the imperial exam,

637
00:24:35,119 --> 00:24:36,400
and they made me raise chickens.

638
00:24:37,359 --> 00:24:38,680
Envy this humble commoner?

639
00:24:39,359 --> 00:24:41,400
That's only because you're not this humble commoner.

640
00:24:41,880 --> 00:24:43,599
If you really became this humble commoner,

641
00:24:44,359 --> 00:24:45,599
you wouldn't have time to cry.

642
00:24:48,640 --> 00:24:50,680
If I really weren't a princess,

643
00:24:50,960 --> 00:24:52,039
then I could...

644
00:25:01,400 --> 00:25:02,200
Never mind.

645
00:25:04,359 --> 00:25:05,160
Tomorrow,

646
00:25:06,400 --> 00:25:08,720
you'll attend the Coronation Ceremony pre-feast.

647
00:25:10,000 --> 00:25:10,920
Get some rest early.

648
00:25:12,440 --> 00:25:13,279
I'll be going now.

649
00:25:20,920 --> 00:25:21,720
Qi Zhi.

650
00:25:21,720 --> 00:25:22,440
Yes?

651
00:25:28,000 --> 00:25:29,359
Thank you.

652
00:25:44,000 --> 00:25:44,680
Tomorrow

653
00:25:44,680 --> 00:25:46,480
will be my Coronation Ceremony.

654
00:25:46,480 --> 00:25:47,519
According to tradition,

655
00:25:47,920 --> 00:25:50,279
I've invited My lords here today

656
00:25:50,359 --> 00:25:51,759
to enjoy the Azure Dragon Dance together.

657
00:25:52,480 --> 00:25:53,440
My lords

658
00:25:53,519 --> 00:25:55,279
are all meritorious servants of Daliang.

659
00:25:55,279 --> 00:25:58,000
I hope My lords will continue to support me,

660
00:25:58,000 --> 00:26:00,359
and build a golden age for Daliang.

661
00:26:02,119 --> 00:26:03,720
Bring the wine.

662
00:26:35,799 --> 00:26:37,400
Eunuch, it's ready.

663
00:27:16,480 --> 00:27:17,279
Come.

664
00:27:17,279 --> 00:27:18,039
My lords,

665
00:27:21,559 --> 00:27:23,359
A toast to the Emperor.

666
00:27:39,559 --> 00:27:41,079
The wine is poisoned.

667
00:27:56,200 --> 00:27:57,000
Come!

668
00:27:57,200 --> 00:27:58,000
Somebody!

669
00:27:58,160 --> 00:27:59,119
Summon the Imperial Physician!

670
00:28:00,440 --> 00:28:01,680
What's the point of summoning the Imperial Physician?

671
00:28:04,319 --> 00:28:05,920
Oh, Your Highness.

672
00:28:06,799 --> 00:28:08,759
No one can help now.

673
00:28:13,200 --> 00:28:14,000
Everyone,

674
00:28:14,960 --> 00:28:15,920
my apologies.

675
00:28:16,880 --> 00:28:19,640
You've all been poisoned by my Bloodbane Pill.

676
00:28:20,640 --> 00:28:21,440
So,

677
00:28:21,880 --> 00:28:25,000
no one is leaving here alive today.

678
00:28:25,039 --> 00:28:25,839
Eunuch Gao,

679
00:28:26,559 --> 00:28:28,039
how could you poison me too?

680
00:28:28,640 --> 00:28:29,440
Give me the antidote, quick!

681
00:28:29,519 --> 00:28:30,440
Shut up!

682
00:28:33,000 --> 00:28:34,039
Xiaoyao,

683
00:28:34,279 --> 00:28:36,640
quit playing the carefree act with me.

684
00:28:41,680 --> 00:28:42,480
Qi Zhi!

685
00:28:45,799 --> 00:28:47,000
Give Huahua back to me!

686
00:28:47,000 --> 00:28:47,799
Oh my,

687
00:28:48,680 --> 00:28:49,880
Special Envoy Qi,

688
00:28:51,279 --> 00:28:53,400
what a deep bond between man and chicken.

689
00:28:55,720 --> 00:28:56,519
Deliver the flower.

690
00:29:08,240 --> 00:29:09,000
Sorry about that,

691
00:29:09,000 --> 00:29:09,799
Special Envoy Qi.

692
00:29:10,079 --> 00:29:11,880
I stewed your dear Huahua.

693
00:29:12,440 --> 00:29:13,480
But tell you what,

694
00:29:13,799 --> 00:29:15,480
before you die, I'll let you

695
00:29:15,519 --> 00:29:17,079
have a taste of chicken.

696
00:29:17,680 --> 00:29:18,480
Please.

697
00:29:20,400 --> 00:29:21,480
You killed Huahua!

698
00:29:21,599 --> 00:29:22,759
I'll fight you to the death!

699
00:29:22,839 --> 00:29:23,640
Don't move!

700
00:29:23,799 --> 00:29:24,559
The more you move,

701
00:29:24,559 --> 00:29:25,720
the faster the poison spreads.

702
00:29:25,720 --> 00:29:26,480
Let go of me!

703
00:29:26,480 --> 00:29:27,599
I'll fight him to the death!

704
00:29:31,000 --> 00:29:32,000
Qi Zhi!

705
00:29:34,920 --> 00:29:35,920
Qi Zhi!

706
00:29:37,480 --> 00:29:38,519
He's dead.

707
00:29:38,680 --> 00:29:39,480
Eunuch Gao,

708
00:29:41,000 --> 00:29:42,799
I grew up by your side since childhood.

709
00:29:43,880 --> 00:29:44,720
I never imagined

710
00:29:45,720 --> 00:29:47,480
you could truly be this vicious.

711
00:29:47,880 --> 00:29:48,519
Qi Zhi!

712
00:29:49,759 --> 00:29:50,880
Crown Prince,

713
00:29:51,720 --> 00:29:54,000
this old servant can't bear to part with you.

714
00:29:54,759 --> 00:29:56,599
Even if you kill us all,

715
00:29:57,559 --> 00:29:59,279
without a puppet to control,

716
00:29:59,279 --> 00:30:01,039
you're still just a lowly servant dog.

717
00:30:01,079 --> 00:30:02,279
We'll see about that.

718
00:30:06,759 --> 00:30:07,240
Hurry!

719
00:30:09,720 --> 00:30:10,799
Don't move!

720
00:30:12,599 --> 00:30:13,039
Come.

721
00:30:13,039 --> 00:30:14,839
This way, please.

722
00:30:18,000 --> 00:30:19,079
This man

723
00:30:19,079 --> 00:30:20,359
is in your hands now.

724
00:30:28,920 --> 00:30:30,359
What I can't have,

725
00:30:31,599 --> 00:30:33,240
none of you will get either.

726
00:30:40,400 --> 00:30:41,799
Why am I here?

727
00:30:43,839 --> 00:30:45,039
I have to thank

728
00:30:45,640 --> 00:30:47,079
that fool Liu Heng.

729
00:30:47,480 --> 00:30:48,759
Who are you calling a fool?

730
00:30:53,400 --> 00:30:54,279
Let me tell you all,

731
00:30:55,039 --> 00:30:55,839
as for you lot,

732
00:30:56,000 --> 00:30:59,279
you drank my Jiu Jiu San Lu Fatal Powder.

733
00:30:59,799 --> 00:31:01,279
After drinking that cup of wine,

734
00:31:01,440 --> 00:31:03,559
day one, your stomach aches for one incense stick.

735
00:31:03,799 --> 00:31:05,640
Day two, two incense sticks of pain.

736
00:31:06,119 --> 00:31:06,960
Take a guess,

737
00:31:07,200 --> 00:31:08,319
what happens on day three?

738
00:31:09,319 --> 00:31:10,960
Three incense sticks of pain, of course!

739
00:31:12,079 --> 00:31:13,000
By then,

740
00:31:13,400 --> 00:31:15,079
when you really can't take it anymore,

741
00:31:15,079 --> 00:31:16,599
you'll beg me to be Emperor.

742
00:31:18,319 --> 00:31:19,319
Let me tell you,

743
00:31:19,640 --> 00:31:20,920
the antidote is right here on me.

744
00:31:21,160 --> 00:31:22,359
If you want to live...

745
00:31:22,359 --> 00:31:23,160
Shut your mouth!

746
00:31:24,839 --> 00:31:26,240
Why are you everywhere I go?

747
00:31:26,880 --> 00:31:28,240
What nonsense are you spouting?

748
00:31:28,640 --> 00:31:30,000
You think you poisoned them?

749
00:31:30,200 --> 00:31:32,599
They were poisoned by this eunuch!

750
00:31:33,440 --> 00:31:34,400
See that?

751
00:31:34,400 --> 00:31:35,720
One's already dead.

752
00:31:37,799 --> 00:31:38,599
Qi Zhi!

753
00:31:38,960 --> 00:31:39,960
Are you okay, Qi Zhi?

754
00:31:40,279 --> 00:31:41,079
Qi Zhi!

755
00:31:44,200 --> 00:31:44,559
Hey,

756
00:31:44,920 --> 00:31:45,720
I just,

757
00:31:45,720 --> 00:31:46,839
forgot to mention this.

758
00:31:47,200 --> 00:31:48,759
I spilled that earlier bowl of wine.

759
00:31:49,119 --> 00:31:50,200
The cup in front of you now,

760
00:31:50,200 --> 00:31:51,160
I swapped it out.

761
00:31:51,160 --> 00:31:52,039
So that means,

762
00:31:52,119 --> 00:31:53,119
the poison in you,

763
00:31:53,119 --> 00:31:54,440
I just put there myself.

764
00:31:54,440 --> 00:31:56,000
It's my poison you're hit with.

765
00:31:56,400 --> 00:31:57,160
Hey!

766
00:31:57,559 --> 00:31:58,640
If you want to live,

767
00:31:59,960 --> 00:32:00,640
you'll all do as I say.

768
00:32:03,279 --> 00:32:04,319
An incense stick passed already?

769
00:32:04,319 --> 00:32:05,079
Stop right there!

770
00:32:05,519 --> 00:32:06,319
Give me the antidote!

771
00:32:06,319 --> 00:32:07,319
No.

772
00:32:07,759 --> 00:32:08,759
Give it!

773
00:32:09,640 --> 00:32:10,640
Okay, okay, here, here, here!

774
00:32:11,440 --> 00:32:11,920
Take it.

775
00:32:19,440 --> 00:32:20,440
Just you wait!

776
00:32:21,480 --> 00:32:23,039
You dared kill Qi Zhi's Huahua!

777
00:32:23,640 --> 00:32:25,000
Today, this princess will kill you!

778
00:32:25,440 --> 00:32:26,079
Get him!

779
00:32:30,920 --> 00:32:31,319
Don't move!

780
00:32:34,160 --> 00:32:34,519
Wait, that's not right.

781
00:32:36,680 --> 00:32:38,599
Didn't I already banish you from the palace?

782
00:32:42,400 --> 00:32:43,400
Eunuch Gao,

783
00:32:44,119 --> 00:32:45,599
I knew something was off about you long ago.

784
00:32:46,839 --> 00:32:47,319
So...

785
00:32:48,200 --> 00:32:50,480
General Li never left the capital at all.

786
00:32:50,640 --> 00:32:51,720
Seize them all!

787
00:32:58,960 --> 00:33:00,279
Nobody come any closer!

788
00:33:00,279 --> 00:33:01,119
Crown Prince, watch out!

789
00:33:02,240 --> 00:33:02,960
You, Li!

790
00:33:02,960 --> 00:33:04,200
Tell your men to leave, now!

791
00:33:04,480 --> 00:33:04,920
Or else...

792
00:33:05,720 --> 00:33:06,759
I'll kill the Crown Prince!

793
00:33:07,160 --> 00:33:09,160
You think you can still walk out of this palace?

794
00:33:09,359 --> 00:33:10,279
Release the Crown Prince now!

795
00:33:10,359 --> 00:33:11,039
You...

796
00:33:11,039 --> 00:33:12,440
As long as you let me out of this palace,

797
00:33:12,440 --> 00:33:13,720
I'll definitely release the Crown Prince.

798
00:33:14,480 --> 00:33:15,839
You're delusional.

799
00:33:16,400 --> 00:33:17,559
The ambush you set up in the palace,

800
00:33:17,559 --> 00:33:18,839
I've already taken care of all of it.

801
00:33:19,599 --> 00:33:21,160
You don't have a single man left to command.

802
00:33:21,839 --> 00:33:23,839
Even if I let you walk out that door,

803
00:33:23,960 --> 00:33:26,240
hundreds of archers wait outside for you.

804
00:33:26,240 --> 00:33:26,960
Stay back!

805
00:33:31,359 --> 00:33:32,440
The throne, in the end,

806
00:33:33,400 --> 00:33:34,599
is just a passing cloud.

807
00:33:35,559 --> 00:33:36,960
As long as you turn back now,

808
00:33:37,880 --> 00:33:39,160
I'm willing to let you off.

809
00:33:39,759 --> 00:33:41,000
I'll let you leave the capital,

810
00:33:41,400 --> 00:33:42,519
let you retire to your hometown. How's that?

811
00:33:42,920 --> 00:33:43,720
Crown Prince,

812
00:33:44,279 --> 00:33:45,039
do you truly mean what you said?

813
00:33:47,200 --> 00:33:48,279
Don't you know me by now?

814
00:33:49,039 --> 00:33:50,279
Would I really lie to you?

815
00:33:50,359 --> 00:33:52,559
Oh, my dear Crown Prince...

816
00:33:52,920 --> 00:33:53,440
Actually, this old servant...

817
00:33:54,039 --> 00:33:55,519
Crown Prince!

818
00:33:56,799 --> 00:33:57,599
Crown Prince!

819
00:33:57,960 --> 00:33:58,759
Crown Prince!

820
00:33:59,599 --> 00:34:00,400
Crown Prince!

821
00:34:00,880 --> 00:34:01,680
Crown Prince!

822
00:34:03,119 --> 00:34:03,920
Crown Prince!

823
00:34:05,799 --> 00:34:06,599
You old scoundrel!

824
00:34:06,720 --> 00:34:07,519
Where do you think you're going?

825
00:34:09,280 --> 00:34:10,079
Crown Prince!

826
00:34:10,519 --> 00:34:11,320
Qi Zhi!

827
00:34:12,519 --> 00:34:13,320
Crown Prince!

828
00:34:14,760 --> 00:34:15,559
Crown Prince!

829
00:34:19,239 --> 00:34:20,280
Crown Prince, wake up!

830
00:34:20,280 --> 00:34:21,079
Crown Prince!

831
00:34:23,599 --> 00:34:24,679
I won.

832
00:34:26,239 --> 00:34:27,400
Crown Prince, what's wrong?

833
00:34:35,519 --> 00:34:36,320
Crown Prince!

834
00:34:36,960 --> 00:34:37,760
Crown Prince!

835
00:34:37,760 --> 00:34:38,800
Old Li tried to kill me.

836
00:34:38,800 --> 00:34:39,960
Crown Prince!

837
00:34:40,880 --> 00:34:41,480
Crown Prince!

838
00:34:42,800 --> 00:34:43,280
Crown Prince!

839
00:34:43,559 --> 00:34:44,960
You absolutely can't die!

840
00:34:46,280 --> 00:34:47,079
Stop!

841
00:34:48,719 --> 00:34:49,519
Crown Prince!

842
00:34:49,800 --> 00:34:50,960
Do you really mean to spare his life?

843
00:34:53,599 --> 00:34:54,920
Just spare his life.

844
00:34:56,079 --> 00:34:56,840
After all,

845
00:34:58,760 --> 00:35:00,599
he doesn't have many years left anyway.

846
00:35:03,440 --> 00:35:04,239
Chicken farmer,

847
00:35:05,800 --> 00:35:06,599
I'm sorry.

848
00:35:07,880 --> 00:35:08,880
I got your Huahua killed.

849
00:35:11,199 --> 00:35:12,000
Right.

850
00:35:12,960 --> 00:35:14,280
So you have to live.

851
00:35:15,119 --> 00:35:17,000
You have to live to pay me back for Huahua, right?

852
00:35:18,320 --> 00:35:19,159
Crown Prince!

853
00:35:19,519 --> 00:35:20,920
Crown Prince, just hold on a bit longer.

854
00:35:21,199 --> 00:35:22,320
The Imperial Physician will be here soon.

855
00:35:24,559 --> 00:35:25,119
Oh, right.

856
00:35:26,440 --> 00:35:27,559
In my study,

857
00:35:28,920 --> 00:35:30,599
there's an unfinished comic book.

858
00:35:32,039 --> 00:35:32,719
Right.

859
00:35:34,119 --> 00:35:34,960
Ouyang Yan,

860
00:35:36,440 --> 00:35:37,400
you have to remember.

861
00:35:38,599 --> 00:35:39,400
I'm sorry.

862
00:35:40,480 --> 00:35:42,280
I can't stay with you till the end.

863
00:35:44,639 --> 00:35:45,320
Hey...

864
00:35:45,320 --> 00:35:45,880
Crown Prince!

865
00:35:46,079 --> 00:35:47,559
Crown Prince!

866
00:35:48,679 --> 00:35:49,239
Crown Prince!

867
00:36:06,079 --> 00:36:07,519
Are you really leaving?

868
00:36:10,280 --> 00:36:11,559
The palace is in chaos right now.

869
00:36:11,880 --> 00:36:13,480
No one cares about Yan Kingdom's affairs.

870
00:36:14,679 --> 00:36:15,480
Let alone

871
00:36:15,480 --> 00:36:16,360
sending troops to help.

872
00:36:19,440 --> 00:36:20,679
Yan Kingdom is in a war crisis.

873
00:36:21,920 --> 00:36:22,760
I have to go.

874
00:36:23,400 --> 00:36:25,280
But what good will it do if you go back alone?

875
00:36:27,440 --> 00:36:28,719
I'm the princess of Yan Kingdom.

876
00:36:29,800 --> 00:36:30,840
I must go back.

877
00:36:31,239 --> 00:36:32,559
What if you weren't the princess?

878
00:36:38,599 --> 00:36:39,760
Unfortunately, there's no "what if."

879
00:36:40,360 --> 00:36:41,159
I'm leaving.

880
00:36:41,679 --> 00:36:42,480
Farewell.
